p: We identified some new compounds which were not reported in these two previous studies. The total yield of these new compounds varied between 2.1 and 5.6% ( Figure 2). The presence of 2,3-dihydro-1,8-cineole (2.1%), ( E)-β-ocimene (2.4%), β-selinene (3.3%), bicyclogermacrene (5.0%), α-amorphene (5.1%), bicyclosesquiphellandrene (5.6%) and γ-curcumene (5.6%) was evidenced.
